{"tid":755040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婦染伊波拉康復一年 傳予家人兒子不治","createTime":"2018-07-25T01:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T03:25:21.000Z","uid":44562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"24d7c52b575babc0bfea1e0f78468b57f4020198","tid":755040,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/774223-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%A9%A6%E6%9F%93%E4%BC%8A%E6%B3%A2%E6%8B%89%E7%97%85%E6%AF%921%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C+%E4%BB%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%82%B3%E6%9F%93%E7%B5%A6%E4%B8%88%E5%A4%AB%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F774223-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E6%259F%2593%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E6%258B%2589%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%25921%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BE%258C%2B%25E4%25BB%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E4%25B8%2588%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590&d=gb6C6Iw906wI3aiqlSyZOMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=49571ef5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F774223-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E6%259F%2593%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E6%258B%2589%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%25921%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BE%258C%2B%25E4%25BB%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E4%25B8%2588%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590&h=5fc75b9b\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/774223-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%A9%A6%E6%9F%93%E4%BC%8A%E6%B3%A2%E6%8B%89%E7%97%85%E6%AF%921%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C+%E4%BB%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%82%B3%E6%9F%93%E7%B5%A6%E4%B8%88%E5%A4%AB%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90</a><br />\n<br />\n非洲利比里亞一名婦人4年前感染了伊波拉病毒，僥倖保住生命及逐漸康復，但她在發病一年後，仍能把病毒傳染給丈夫及兩名兒子，其中1名兒子更不幸死亡。這宗病例顯示伊波拉病毒可以在人體存活一段長時間，而且仍然有傳播能力。<br />\n<br />\n醫生和研究人員在周二出版的《刺針傳染病》醫學期刊內發表報告，指該名婦人於2014年7月患病，確診感染了伊波拉病毒，接受治療後逐漸康復。到2015年11月19日，她的15歲兒子也被診斷對伊波拉病毒呈陽性反應，並於四天後死去。<br />\n<br />\n醫生發現，該名婦人的丈夫（即死去男童的父親）和另一名8歲兒子，同樣對伊波拉病毒呈陽性反應，並出現疲倦、頭痛及發燒等癥狀。醫生再度該名婦人進行檢驗，再找不到伊波拉病毒的蹤跡，但她體內有抗體，是她對上一次患病後產生的抗體。她現時已有對抗這種病毒的免疫能力。　該對夫婦還有一名寶寶，同樣被驗出體內有抗體，可能是媽媽為他餵哺母乳時，把抗體傳給他。<br />\n<br />\n醫學界專家說，雖然這是一宗罕見病例，但卻顯示出伊波拉病人即使已經康復，仍需要接受長期監察，這一點十分重要。醫學界認為這宗罕見個案顯示病毒或會避過免疫系統攻擊，潛伏患者體內。<br />\n<br />\n伊波拉病毒於2014年在非洲大爆發，利比里亞是其中一個嚴重疫區。當局於2015年5月宣布該國已經沒有人傳人的個案。專家相信，這家人的幾宗個案是2014年那次大爆發的延續"},{"pid":"651849e371d6fa40c6b63b62825860c96dc56ad8","tid":755040,"uid":69794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:48:08.000Z","msg":"28 weeks later<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c84d28856f35a8c50402717eb015f97dc2bca0","tid":755040,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"咁叫唔叫康復？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2178da458eedb86f08285547cc53848d8ce2ee30","tid":755040,"uid":41382,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"26c84d28856f35a8c50402717eb015f97dc2bca0","tid":755040,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"咁叫唔叫康復？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:51:32.000Z","msg":"個病人已經康復有抗體，但仍然係帶菌者咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05439f21c60ff6aa5e74ab7d449245153122213","tid":755040,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26c84d28856f35a8c50402717eb015f97dc2bca0","tid":755040,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"咁叫唔叫康復？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:51:52.000Z","msg":"個女人一早死咗會唔會仲好啲 ?"},{"pid":"5b7ea9f86671dc4847fa09f659657918e8a32513","tid":755040,"uid":60164,